HEADWORD: Moorish
<hw>Moor"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From 2d <er>Moor</er>.]</ety>
<def>Having the characteristics of a moor or heath.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Moorish</xex> fens.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Thomson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
